{"data":[{"date":"21:15 21/07","title":"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-ly-giai-that-bai-cua-hagl-tren-san-vinh.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn.</h2><h2>HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho c\u01a1n m\u01b0a t\u1ea1i Vinh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/HLV-Duong-Minh-Ninh-ly-giai-that-bai-cua-HAGL-tren-san-Vinh-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng CLB HAGL kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00ec y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 21/7, CLB HAGL c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh g\u1eb7p CLB SLNA. V\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 SLNA khai th\u00e1c tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3. V\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 3-1 chung cu\u1ed9c nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh \u0111\u00fang c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 cho r\u1eb1ng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Chi\u1ec1u nay, tr\u1eddi ch\u01b0a m\u01b0a l\u00fac kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng. Khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u00f3 c\u01a1n m\u01b0a nh\u1ecf l\u00e0m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecb thua. \u1ede hi\u1ec7p 2, khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u00e2ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u00e2ng cao khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thua th\u00eam b\u00e0n n\u1eefa\", HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho bi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng HAGL c\u0169ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201c\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi hai ngo\u1ea1i binh c\u1ee7a SLNA l\u00e0 Olaha v\u00e0 Lynch Jermine. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olaha t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t khi ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, v\u00e0 h\u00e0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tung Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb \u0111au g\u1ed1i nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra lo l\u1eafng khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, song \u00f4ng hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n t\u1eadp trung trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-hagl-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191726.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/slna-vs-hagl-vong-20-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-hagl-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191726.html\">SLNA 3-1 HAGL (KT): \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 8 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf V-League 2018</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i HAGL v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 3-1, SLNA \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u00e2ng chu\u1ed7i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 8, qua \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m tranh ch\u1ea5p huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4470","checkdouble":"191750"},{"date":"21:32 21/07","title":"H\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p HAGL, SLNA b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c V-League 13 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/ha-dep-hagl-slna-bat-kip-ky-luc-vleague-13-nam-truoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 v\u1eeba b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i 13 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i V-League do CLB G\u1ea1ch \u0110\u1ed3ng T\u00e2m Long An thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL.</h2><h2>SLNA b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c V-League sau 13 n\u0103m</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League, CLB SLNA \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 HAGL. V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch to\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai t\u1ea1i \u2018ch\u1ea3o l\u1eeda\u2019 Vinh \u1edf 3 m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t cao trong th\u1eddi gian qua, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i HAGL.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p HAGL, SLNA b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c V-League 13 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p HAGL, SLNA b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c V-League 13 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/6_Zing_3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>SLNA ch\u1ea1m m\u1ed1c k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh Olaha sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdc khe th\u00f4ng minh c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c. Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 HAGL c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2 nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa SLNA \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e1i l\u1eadp kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 2 b\u00e0n nh\u1edd pha ch\u1edbp c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n To\u00e0n\u00a0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3-1 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00fap SLNA gi\u00e0nh tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 8 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. N\u00f3 c\u0169ng gi\u00fap h\u1ecd san b\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh 8 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i 13 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i V-League do CLB G\u1ea1ch \u0110\u1ed3ng T\u00e2m Long An thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp t\u1ea1i V-League 2005.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n th\u1eafng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa, SLNA s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i V-League. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1edfi \u1edf v\u00f2ng 21, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u00e0ng th\u00eam ch\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t khi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao v\u1eabn c\u00f2n g\u1ea7n hai th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 SLNA chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Sau v\u00f2ng 20 n\u00e0y, V-League 2018 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1m ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eadp trung. V\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 21 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 8/9 t\u1edbi.\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4469","checkdouble":"191752"},{"date":"06:30 22/07","title":"Thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HLV FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/thua-nguoc-clb-ha-noi-hlv-flc-thanh-hoa-phai-thua-nhan-mot-su-that.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</h2><h2>HLV FLC Thanh H\u00f3a th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i qu\u00e1 tinh qu\u00e1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/video-tong-hop-thanh-hoa-23-ha-noi-vong-20-vleague-2018.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u00a0FLC Thanh H\u00f3a l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League gi\u1eefa FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 21/7, ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, song nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Thanh H\u00f3a b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi t\u1eadp trung \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam Nguy\u1ec5n Thanh Chung ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf ph\u00fat 64 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00fap H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 3-2. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y, HLV FLC Thanh H\u00f3a Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1eafng. Ba b\u00e0n thua t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh \u0111\u00fang th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 42 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. \u00d4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u1ec1 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi, song h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tinh qu\u00e1i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. C\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung \u1edf nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng hai, trong khi CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 tinh qu\u00e1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y hai c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0 l\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00fat ra qua nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u00f3 t\u00e2m th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 trong tay 51 \u0111i\u1ec3m. H\u1ecd \u0111ang h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a t\u1edbi 17 \u0111i\u1ec3m. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00ean ng\u00f4i sau 1, 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ed1p nh\u1eadn huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/21/Highlight-Thanh-Hoa-vs-Ha-Noi.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4468","checkdouble":"191753"},{"date":"22:32 21/07","title":"Li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/lien-tiep-toa-sang-tien-linh-van-chua-nghi-toi-cuoc-chay-dua-voi-tien-linh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh.</h2><h2>Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i V-Leauge</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 21/7, t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n G\u00f2 \u0110\u1eadu \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai CLB Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u00e0n so g\u0103ng gi\u1eefa hai ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Ti\u1ebfn Linh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1997 v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u1ed9i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t V-League 2018 cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ASIAD. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 tin khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng duy tr\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng cho B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng chi\u1ec1u nay, Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 11. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Oseni c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 3 b\u00e0n. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, d\u00f9 \u2018t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i\u2019 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y song ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u1ea3 Ti\u1ebfn Linh v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n mang theo tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 115%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4467","checkdouble":"191754"},{"date":"06:30 22/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-1 c\u1ee7a SLNA tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/21/nhung-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-thang-cua-slna-truoc-hagl.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, CLB SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>1. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u0103ng hoa th\u1eddi gian qua, CLB SLNA \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 HAGL. V\u00e0 nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn&nbsp;SLNA 3-1 HAGL, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 ba V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc, Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n B\u00ecnh \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Olaha \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap SLNA t\u1ea1o ra th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Olaha \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 13 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa SLNA \u0111\u00e3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n HAGL v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn SLNA 3-1 HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn SLNA 3-1 HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/Nhung-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-SLNA-3-1-HAGL-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>SLNA gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. Sai l\u1ea7m chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a HAGL<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tung c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00edt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 Phan Thanh H\u1eadu v\u00e0o s\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng trong hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh H\u1eadu kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00ec \u0111\u00e8 t\u1ecf ra l\u1ea1c l\u00f5ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng HAGL. V\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng s\u1eeda sai khi tung ngo\u1ea1i binh Osmar v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 V\u0103n To\u00e0n ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 46 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00ec \u0111\u00e8 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng di chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Osmar c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ee9c \u00e9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb hi\u1ec7p 1, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd HAGL \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trong nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Vinh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp 8 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn SLNA 3-1 HAGL, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i V-League 2018 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1eaft m\u1eb7t, r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 xu\u1ed1ng 1-2 cho HAGL. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf n\u00ean s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m HAGL t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi SLNA. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y song c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 an \u1ee7i nho nh\u1ecf khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi SLNA t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Vinh sau 8 m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, trong c\u00e1c chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ecb chia \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1eb7c t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n l\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-1 c\u1ee7a SLNA tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-1 c\u1ee7a SLNA tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Nhung-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-thang-3-1-cua-SLNA-truoc-HAGL-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh trong 8 n\u0103m qua</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. Ti\u1ebfc cho Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a SLNA, trung v\u1ec7 Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u pha \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n c\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi hai l\u1ea7n c\u1eaft b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ch\u00e2n ngo\u1ea1i binh Osmar c\u1ee7a HAGL, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee9u nguy cho khung th\u00e0nh SLNA.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 SLNA, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n kh\u00f4ng \u00edt C\u0110V t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 su\u1ea5t cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c mu\u1ed1n \u01b0u ti\u00ean cho c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y Park &lsquo;ng\u00f3 l\u01a1&rsquo; Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00e1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i b\u1edfi \u0111ang \u1edf th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao phong \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng, ng\u00f4i sao SLNA ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ed1t ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u00e1ng tin tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.</p>\r\n5. C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thay nhau t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c khi anh chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng tinh t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 ngo\u1ea1i binh Olaha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n. \u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng song anh l\u1ea1i k\u00e9m duy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c &lsquo;t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i&rsquo; th\u00ec c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh l\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. L\u00e0 m\u1eabu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi HLV Park Hang Seo sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"SLNA vs HAGL\" title=\"SLNA vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/bna_vantoan9414827_2172018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n To\u00e0n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u1edf tr\u1eadn SLNA 3-1 HAGL</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n c\u0169ng k\u1ecbp ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y b\u00ean ph\u00eda HAGL. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, V\u0103n To\u00e0n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t ra s\u00e2n cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 V\u0103n To\u00e0n, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y th\u00ec 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp nh\u01b0 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, V\u0103n Thanh,&hellip; s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i trong danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. S\u1ebd c\u00f3 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp trung s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: SLNA 3-1 HAGL</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ghi b\u00e0n:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SLNA: Olaha 13', Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh 45'+2, Xu\u00e2n To\u00e0n 68'</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL: C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng 46'</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SLNA: V\u0169 H\u1ea3i; Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u00ecnh Ho\u00e0ng, V\u0103n Kh\u00e1nh, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh, Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc, Xu\u00e2n To\u00e0n, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Jeremie Lynch, Michael Olaha</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL: V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng; V\u0103n S\u01a1n, V\u0103n Thanh, Zeba Josip, A Ho\u00e0ng, Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, A S\u00e2n, Phan Thanh H\u1eadu, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Zeba<br>\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-ly-giai-that-bai-cua-hagl-tren-san-vinh-168-191750.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-ly-giai-that-bai-cua-hagl-tren-san-vinh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-ly-giai-that-bai-cua-hagl-tren-san-vinh-168-191750.html\">HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4466","checkdouble":"191757"},{"date":"20:45 21/07","title":"\"Kylian Mbappe l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/16/bakayoko-mbappe-la-cau-thu-tot-nhat-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Kylian Mbappe t\u1ea1i \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tiemoue Bakayoko \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><h2>Bakayoko ng\u1ee3i khen t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a\u00a0Kylian Mbappe</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 19, Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. V\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u00edt pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bakayoko Kylian Mbappe l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bakayoko Kylian Mbappe l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/bakayoko-mbappe-la-cau-thu-tot-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Mbappe th\u0103ng hoa t\u1ea1i World Cup, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Tiemoue Bakayoko \u0111\u00e3 cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat PSG l\u00fac n\u00e0y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean t\u1edd Goal, Bakayoko cho hay: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Mbappe.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng gi\u00e0 d\u1eb7n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 t\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u00f3, Mbappe \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Bakayoko v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Mbappe v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bakayoko, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p Raphael Varane c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng m\u1ef9 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Mbappe. Varane m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \"ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u00e0i h\u00e0nh tinh\", v\u00e0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u2018h\u1ecdc m\u1ed9t bi\u1ebft m\u01b0\u1eddi\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV Deschamps c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng Mbappe xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n Henry th\u1eddi tr\u1ebb. \u201c\"N\u0103m 1998, Thierry Henry v\u00e0 David Trezeguet \u1edf c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i Kylian Mbappe l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Mbappe. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb s\u1edbm. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, nh\u01b0ng Mbappe c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n th\u1ebf. Th\u1eadt may v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean Mbappe v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i PSG \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mbappe n\u00f3i tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0i\u00a0TF1: \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG. Trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 m\u00e3n khi l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng minh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. C\u1ee9 sau m\u1ed7i n\u0103m, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh cho PSG\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:#222222;mso-fareast-language:ko\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4465","checkdouble":"191747"},{"date":"20:32 21/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 21/7: Cho\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 kinh ho\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/7/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-217-choang-voi-muc-gia-kinh-hoang-cua-hang-thai-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 21/7.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Cho\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 kinh ho\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i M.U<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB Crystal Palace \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 ng\u00f4i sao Wilfred Zaha t\u1edbi&hellip; 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Tottenham, Chelsea v\u00e0 Everton. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i M.U, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 217 Cho\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 217 Cho\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/crystal-palace-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-man-city-va-tottenham-vu-zaha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 21/7: Zaha c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>M.U quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn Barca v\u00ec sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Adrien Rabiot. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca, v\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Hi\u1ec7n nay, c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u00e0 Rabiot l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean r\u1ea5t gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real quy\u1ebft chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Hazard<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean 125 tri\u1ec7u euro b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n t\u1eeb b\u1ecf ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chia tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 200 tri\u1ec7u euro (kho\u1ea3ng 176 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng). B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng \u0111ang h\u1ecfi mua Kieran Trippier v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai James Rodriguez<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Real Madrid, tuy nhi\u00ean Bayern Munich quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n anh v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Hi\u1ec7n nay, James v\u1eabn g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi H\u00f9m x\u00e1m theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 2 n\u0103m, sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 6/2019 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 21/7\" title=\"James Rodriguez ghi ban truoc Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/2/Nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-Real-2-2-Bayern-ban-ket-C1-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>James Rodriguez kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Bayern h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Roma mong ch\u1edd ng\u00e0y t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Alisson<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson Becker \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi ch\u00fac may m\u1eafn t\u1eeb HLV Roma &ndash; \u00f4ng Di Francesco. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i Alisson \u1edf Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4464","checkdouble":"191748"},{"date":"21:46 21/07","title":"Deschamps: \"C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng h\u01a1n Ronaldo, Messi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/deschamps-cac-hoc-tro-cua-toi-xung-dang-gianh-bong-vang-hon-ronaldo-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110T v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u2013 Didier Deschamps ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng, sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nDeschamps mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng, nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i. Antoine Griezmann gi\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i World Cup (sau Modric v\u00e0 Hazard), trong khi Kylian Mbappe l\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb hay nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Paul Pogba c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, v\u00e0 Raphael Varane \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed khi gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 World Cup l\u1eabn Champions League trong v\u00f2ng 1 n\u0103m. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, HLV Deschamps cho r\u1eb1ng, ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean t\u1edd L&rsquo;Equipe, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Antoine l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng cho danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u00ecnh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Antoine r\u1ea5t x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi n\u00f3. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu Antoine chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y, d\u00f9 ch\u00fang ta lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 2 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn c\u1ea1nh tranh h\u00e0ng n\u0103m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\"><br>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Deschamps ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng\" title=\"HLV Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p sau World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/deschamps-cac-hoc-tro-cua-toi-xung-dang-gianh-bong-vang-hon-ronaldo-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Deschamps ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Neymar c\u0169ng v\u1eady, ngay c\u1ea3 khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y x\u1ebfp sau Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi. Raphael Varane c\u00f3 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng kh\u00f4ng? T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 c\u00f3, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m World Cup v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Kylian m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 19 tu\u1ed5i. Ch\u00fang ta th\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. \u1ede \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f3, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Kylian l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00fat n\u00e0o. Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eebng h\u1ecfi v\u00ec sao t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&rdquo; &ndash; Deschamps ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2007 v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Kaka, 10 n\u0103m qua c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ph\u00e1t ch\u00e1n v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi thay nhau d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft ch\u1eebng, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a 2 si\u00eau sao n\u00e0y d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhin-lai-thanh-cong-cua-tuyen-phap-mau-chot-la-su-doan-ket-421-191524.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/nhin-lai-thanh-cong-cua-tuyen-phap-mau-chot-la-su-doan-ket.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhin-lai-thanh-cong-cua-tuyen-phap-mau-chot-la-su-doan-ket-421-191524.html\">Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: M\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft</span><br>\r\n&ldquo;L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u00e2u Phi gi\u00e0nh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng&rdquo; &ndash; B\u1ea1n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 nghe qua l\u1eddi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ec9a mai n\u00e0y, khi \u0110T Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/doi-truong-phap-tiet-lo-dieu-dac-biet-sau-chien-thang-truoc-argentina-421-191641.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/doi-truong-phap-tiet-lo-dieu-dac-biet-sau-chien-thang-truoc-argentina.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/doi-truong-phap-tiet-lo-dieu-dac-biet-sau-chien-thang-truoc-argentina-421-191641.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina</span><br>\r\nHugo Lloris ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4463","checkdouble":"191751"},{"date":"19:03 21/07","title":"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n CLB mu\u1ed1n thanh l\u00fd Giroud \u201cgi\u00fap\u201d Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/9/atletico-muon-co-giroud-tu-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Atletico mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Giroud trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft ph\u00eda Chelsea c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Giroud h\u1ebft ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ti\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho HLV Antonio Conte. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, h\u1ecd m\u1eddi m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Maurizio Sarri v\u1ec1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft. Sau m\u00f9a 2017/18, Sarri \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Napoli thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng Carlo Ancelotti.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi Chelsea, Sarri h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. The Blues m\u1edbi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Jorginho, h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a Sarri t\u1ea1i Napoli. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 linh h\u1ed3n trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u1edf \u0111o\u1ea1n ng\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Atletico mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Giroud trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Atletico mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Giroud trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/14/Atletico-muon-co-Giroud-trong-mua-he-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Giroud</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSarri \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Gonzalo Higuain, h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 khi c\u00f2n \u1edf Napoli v\u1ec1 Chelsea. Khi h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c m\u00f9a 2015/16, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina ghi t\u1edbi 38 b\u00e0n sau 42 tr\u1eadn. V\u00e0 khi Chelsea nh\u1eafm Higuain, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Olivier Giroud b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Atletico mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Giroud</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Conte, Giroud gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea t\u1eeb Arsenal \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018 v\u00e0 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, sau khi Sarri t\u1edbi, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i l\u00e0 Alvaro Morata l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ngoi sao Griezmann Atletico\" title=\"ngoi sao Griezmann Atletico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/10/costa-phat-bieu-ve-griezmann-va-hop-dong-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Atletico mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Giroud \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Griezmann</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi Chelsea thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0111o\u1ea1n ng\u1eafn, Giroud \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng th\u00edch nghi. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c anh ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Higuain.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Atletico Madrid ng\u1ecf \u00fd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Giroud. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Giroud - Antoine Griezmann t\u1eebng gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Griezmann d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barcelona ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o d\u1eef \u0111\u1ed9i song sau c\u00f9ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi Atletico.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jeremie-boga-roi-chelsea-toi-sassuolo-172-191736.html\">T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/100-golovin-cap-ben-chelsea-o-he-2018-172-191734.html\">100% Golovin c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bi-mat-dam-phan-mua-higuain-172-191728.html\">Chelsea b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi thay Morata</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nham-joe-hart-thay-courtois-172-191722.html\">C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi c\u00e1i t\u00ean Chelsea nh\u1eafm thay Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-se-ban-kante-cho-psg-neu-172-191721.html\">Chelsea s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Kante cho PSG n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4462","checkdouble":"191744"},{"date":"21:18 21/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Colombia quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u00e1m tr\u1ee5 t\u1ea1i Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/nguoi-hung-colombia-quyet-tam-bam-tru-tai-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Premier League, nh\u01b0ng trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina quy\u1ebft \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMina quy\u1ebft b\u00e1m tr\u1ee5 ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap Colombia l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8, trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barcelona, anh v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb g\u1eedi \u0111i cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u0169 kh\u00ed l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Barca v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng Pique, Umtiti v\u00e0 Vermaelen thay nhau \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3, G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia m\u1edbi \u0111em v\u1ec1 Clement Lenglet t\u1eeb Sevilla, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mina quy\u1ebft \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y\" title=\"Mina quy\u1ebft \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/nguoi-hung-colombia-quyet-tam-bam-tru-tai-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mina quy\u1ebft \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Everton l\u00e0 CLB mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Mina. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Barca. Hi\u1ec7n nay, t\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 khi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay, Yerry Mina gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou t\u1eeb Palmeiras v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 11,8 tri\u1ec7u euro (11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng). Anh \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, c\u00f9ng chi ph\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 100 tri\u1ec7u euro. V\u00ec v\u1eady, HLV Ernesto Valverde d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, v\u00ec v\u1eady l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Barca s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i theo d\u00f5i s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Colombia trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Yerry Mina quy\u1ebft \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng anh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang-172-191729.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang-172-191729.html\">&ldquo;H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i&rdquo; Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi mua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn</span><br>\r\nEverton mu\u1ed1n mua Lucas Digne c\u1ee7a Barcelona v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh dung c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-quan-tam-toi-jasper-cillessen-172-191681.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/9/10/ter-stegen-chan-thuong-cillessen-som-ra-mat-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-quan-tam-toi-jasper-cillessen-172-191681.html\">S\u1ee3 Real c\u01b0\u1edbp ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Chelsea v\u1ed9i v\u00e3 h\u1ecfi mua sao Barca</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a CLB Real Madrid cho th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Thibaut Courtois, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1eafm m\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. V\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4461","checkdouble":"191745"},{"date":"05:23 22/07","title":"Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \"h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" c\u1ee7a Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/12/20/barca-bat-ngo-muon-ky-hop-dong-voi-hang-thai-cua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Simon Mignolet t\u1edbi Barca l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1eafm h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u1ebfu Jasper Cillessen ra \u0111i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Simon Mignolet t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eddi Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Simon Mignolet \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0o tay Karius. Su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a 2017/18 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c Simon Mignolet t\u1edbi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c Simon Mignolet t\u1edbi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/16/Cuc-soc-Simon-Mignolet-toi-Barca-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Mignolet mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Alisson</span> t\u1eeb Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, Mignolet l\u00fac n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 3 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Sunderland \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi Anfield \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Simon Mignolet kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111ang t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cLiverpool b\u1ecf ra g\u1ea7n 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, Mignolet bi\u1ebft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra \u0111i. Liverpool c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mignolet c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Simon Mignolet t\u1edbi Barca l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1eafm h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u1ebfu Jasper Cillessen ra\u00a0\u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mignolet\" title=\"Mignolet\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/9/24/Leicester-2-3-Liverpool-Mot-ke-noi-loan-de-lam-nen-su-khac-biet-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mignolet c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCillessen hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli. N\u1ebfu th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan s\u1ebd chi 8 \u0111\u1ebfn\u00a010 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Mignolet. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Alisson v\u00e0 Karius, The Kop s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 cho Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Marc-Andre ter Stegen r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Mignolet c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh, anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb s\u1ed1 1 cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn c\u00fap nh\u00e0 Vua T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nico Vaesen c\u1ee7a Mignolet n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1edbi Barca: \u201cC\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Mignolet s\u1ebd c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4460","checkdouble":"191758"},{"date":"05:37 22/07","title":"\"V\u1edbi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Welbeck l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/voi-15-trieu-bang-welbeck-la-mon-hoi-voi-moi-doi-bong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Danny Welbeck r\u1eddi Arsenal l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Ray Parlor kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ef1u sao M.U s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Welbeck v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Danny Welbeck c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Wenger, song nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf s\u00e2n Emirates trong 4 n\u0103m qua l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n Danny Welbeck r\u1eddi Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n Danny Welbeck r\u1eddi Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/HLV-Unai-Emery-muon-Danny-Welbeck-roi-Arsenal-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Danny Welbeck&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 ra s\u00e2n 80 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Arsenal nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 ghi 15 b\u00e0n, anh ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London. Nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/welbeck-va-ospina-sap-bi-hlv-emery-tong-khoi-arsenal-172-191482.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Arsenal b\u00e1n Welbeck</span> \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. V\u1edbi Lacazette v\u00e0 Aubameyang, c\u1ef1u HLV PSG kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Welbeck.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDaily Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd b\u1ecf ra 16 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1eeb M.U. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Welbeck s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Emery d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Welbeck l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Welbeck r\u1eddi Arsenal l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Ray Parlor kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ef1u sao M.U s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Welbeck CSKA 2-2 Arsenal\" title=\"Welbeck CSKA 2-2 Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/CSKA-2-2-Arsenal-Khi-Arsene-Wenger-nghi-qua-nhieu-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ray Parlor cho r\u1eb1ng&nbsp;</span>Welbeck l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Welbeck kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ea1i M.U v\u00e0 Arsenal. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t, Welbeck ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi kho\u1ea3ng 15 \u0111\u1ebfn 20 b\u00e0n \u1edf NHA n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi qu\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 28, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb. N\u1ebfu Welbeck \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm. N\u1ebfu chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng, nh\u01b0ng 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng th\u00ec kh\u00e1c&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;N\u1ebfu Arsenal mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Welbeck, nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh s\u1ebd h\u1ecfi mua c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. V\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4459","checkdouble":"191759"},{"date":"06:06 22/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Gareth Bale?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/mu-khong-co-kha-nang-chieu-mo-gareth-bale-vi-tien-luong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Gareth Bale th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Liverpool v\u00e0 Man City, Craig Bellamy.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Gareth Bale</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh HLV Jose Mourinho quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gareth Bale c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua Gareth Bale M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf Bale t\u1edbi Old Trafford h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mua Gareth Bale M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf Bale t\u1edbi Old Trafford h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/mu-khong-co-kha-nang-chieu-mo-gareth-bale-vi-tien-luong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Craig Bellamy tin r\u1eb1ng M.U kh\u00f4ng mua\u00a0</span>Bale v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Lopetegui v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu. Tuy nhi\u00ean, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-gareth-bale-neu-172-191511.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bale s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Real Madrid</span> n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Gareth Bale th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Liverpool v\u00e0 Man City, Craig Bellamy.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. M.U l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Bale \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi. N\u1ebfu M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Bale \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 CLB m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cBale kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Bale, song ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cJuventus \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 mua Ronaldo v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao, song gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, Bale kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3n n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bale h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Craig Bellamy tin r\u1eb1ng Gareth Bale s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bale Ronaldo\" title=\"Bale Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/8/8/real-madrid-len-ke-hoach-troi-chan-4-sao-khung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Craig Bellamy kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh\u00a0</span>Bale h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo r\u1eddi Bernabeu</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cS\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Bale. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Ronaldo che ph\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Bale l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi vui nh\u1ea5t khi Ronaldo quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Juventus\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cBale \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi Bale s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4458","checkdouble":"191761"}]}